### 6. **Image File Conversion Utility**

**File:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775496965350-86o4fo/packages/provider-utils/src/convert-image-model-file-to-data-uri.ts`

