**File:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775496965350-86o4fo/packages/provider/src/image-model-middleware/v3/image-model-v3-middleware.ts`

